# Placeholder for figures directory

User should place all report figures (PNG/PDF) in this directory.

Supported image formats:
- PNG (recommended)
- PDF (vector)
- JPG

Usage in LaTeX:
\includegraphics[width=0.8\textwidth]{figures/filename.png}

Example figures to add:
- architecture-diagram.png
- sequence-diagram-find-route.png
- ui-station-mode.png
- ui-map-mode.png
- benchmark-chart-explored-nodes.png
- use-case-diagram.png
- data-model-diagram.png
